    "content": "The UN SDGs have moved from a high-level framework to a practical roadmap for the private sector. In real estate, this means every investment decision can be mapped to a specific goal. Are we promoting clean energy (SDG 7)? Are we ensuring clean water and sanitation (SDG 6)? Are we building inclusive and safe communities (SDG 11)? By using the SDGs as our guide, we ensure our capital is deployed with purpose and that our impact is measurable, verifiable, and aligned with a global vision for a better future."
